core:assignAction.core:comment: If we have converted the barcode from RJ format, we must be running in a mixed estate. In this case the transaction barcode will not necessarily match the transaction id, so we must optionally perform a search based on the branch, terminal and transaction numbers as well.

core:outcomeLink.core:comment: Comment Note. If the list is not null at this point then the list must have zero entries, which means no match and its not an error
